  Stable for x86, wrt bug #550568

  28 May 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org>
  cernlib-montecarlo-2006-r3.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #550568

  27 May 2015; Andrew Savchenko <bircoph@gentoo.org>
